LibUseful is currently managed through a repo at github: https://github.com/ColumPaget/libUseful

Please note that any contributions must be releasable under the Lesser GPL v3, as libUseful can be built under either the GPLv3 or Lesser GPLv3, but the Lesser GPLv3 covers most of the code.

Thanks go to the following for their contributions:

